      "type": "message",
      "text": "Does anyone know examples (or name of the pattern) of markup formats where instead of writing format directives _inline_ &lt;b&gt;like this&lt;/b&gt; you do it _out-of-the-line_ like:\n\n```text writing format directives inline like this\n bold like this```\n",
